                     <decoNote type="initial">Occasional large ornamented initials, especially
                        at the front and back of the manuscript.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="initial">Ornamented initials: 235r, 268r, 272r. </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="initial">Initials in red: 66v </decoNote>
